!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>has been very reliable</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sophiac2/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dff8d4f9c11298d173209cff06fa10fc13e7a985398f2aef4f25b755f521ee5a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dff8d4f9c11298d173209cff06fa10fc13e7a985398f2aef4f25b755f521ee5a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sophiac2/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sophiac2</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 3, 2026</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Very, very helpful so far.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/csdshop/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1bdaeab84c535abcfa93e4f3844fb7aa1edcfd9386be35784e3c0c53224c2859?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1bdaeab84c535abcfa93e4f3844fb7aa1edcfd9386be35784e3c0c53224c2859?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/csdshop/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Stefano <small>(csdshop)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 2, 2026</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We had a problem on the button \"pubblish\", after an update we resolve it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thank you so much!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fast and Super Helpful</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/christie212/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10000f766551bf9f6d4ac690aa771e7c718210eccd6634cb68fa535fbb87e0ba?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10000f766551bf9f6d4ac690aa771e7c718210eccd6634cb68fa535fbb87e0ba?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/christie212/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">christie212</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 1, 2026</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Had a few problems with my site but Frank Remmy and Shahzeen were super helpful and replied quickly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good but Heavy</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lizahamid/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8100921781351b6a49e75ece6e35d7f1b2644e71f67ce14a993e1bfcc963ad1f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8100921781351b6a49e75ece6e35d7f1b2644e71f67ce14a993e1bfcc963ad1f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lizahamid/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lizahamid</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 1, 2026</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Works well for online stores n has lots of features. But feels a bit heavy n setup takes time. Once done, it runs fine tho 👍</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Super fast support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dziudek/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec3db6152e60dd4ffbcaacd2b0af93ce81530d1f83781697380f5edf2f4ada96?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec3db6152e60dd4ffbcaacd2b0af93ce81530d1f83781697380f5edf2f4ada96?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dziudek/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Tomasz Dziuda <small>(dziudek)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 30, 2026</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Very helpful for my case :) </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Quick and Effective Spport</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cav949241/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/25755c521bda7386ed870cd7ed78eea122aaf2b46b8c5f337d7f839d8fd99e7d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/25755c521bda7386ed870cd7ed78eea122aaf2b46b8c5f337d7f839d8fd99e7d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cav949241/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cav949241</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 26, 2026</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Very impressive response time </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Han resuelto los problemas con la actualización</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/esteticadirecto/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a1f4407fbe53220b001120f275d58a612686e32eca79b745bab91baf11069ace?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a1f4407fbe53220b001120f275d58a612686e32eca79b745bab91baf11069ace?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/esteticadirecto/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">esteticadirecto</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 23, 2026</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rápidas respuestas.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Gracias.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fast service</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/funique/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/45af76fa502c6629536327560b6193060d68c54e3c810a0331998040f2a65e37?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/45af76fa502c6629536327560b6193060d68c54e3c810a0331998040f2a65e37?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/funique/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">funique</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 20, 2026</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I had a tiny problem with email formatting, the custom header was nor replacing the placeholder one. had a fast reply and the solution was activating and reactivating theme and resaving once or twice!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:146:\"Everything you need to launch an online store in days and keep it growing for years. From your first sale to millions in revenue, Woo is with you.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.10.6.2.zip\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:6:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=3234504\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=3234504\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=3234504\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=3235205\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=3234504\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-6.png?rev=3234504\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:9:\"ecommerce\";s:9:\"ecommerce\";s:12:\"online-store\";s:12:\"online store\";s:11:\"sell-online\";s:11:\"sell online\";s:4:\"shop\";s:4:\"shop\";s:13:\"shopping-cart\";s:13:\"shopping cart\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:620:{s:6:\"10.0.0\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.10.0.0.zip\";s:11:\"10.0.0-rc.1\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wooco